      "description": "Richardson extrapolation performed on three mesh densities (2.1 M, 5.8 M, 14.2 M elements). Grid convergence index (GCI) for NIH quantity of interest is 3.2% on the fine mesh, satisfying the MRL 2 discretization error threshold of GCI < 5%.",
      "validationMetric": "Grid Convergence Index (GCI)",
      "outcome": "Pass",
      "comparisonError": 0.032
    },
