    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The CFD hemolysis model demonstrates adequate predictive accuracy at the validated mid-range operating point (NIH relative error 6.8%). Mesh convergence, solver convergence, and software QA are confirmed. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 criterion is satisfied across all five COU operating points in simulation. The credibility assessment team accepts the model for the stated COU.",
